data.description: Welcome Home! Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a wealth of desirable features--this property is a true gem! Upon entry, you're greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The home's layout includes a formal dining room, ideal for hosting gatherings and creating cherished memories with family and friends! The heart of the home lies in the spacious living room adorned by a fireplace with a charming brick mantle. The primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom that features a beautifully designed custom-tiled shower, offering a serene retreat after a long day. The additional bedrooms are generously sized, providing ample space for family members or guests. This home has no carpet throughout ensuring easy maintenance! Stepping outside, you'll discover an entertainer's paradise. Exterior features include a large backyard, a conveniently located half bathroom & an in-ground pool that's perfect for enjoying those hot Louisiana Summers! A covered patio provides the perfect spot to savor the outdoors and entertain guests. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your dream home!
